---
import kittyGif from "@/assets/images/kitty.gif";
---

<section id="story" class="section" aria-labelledby="story-title">
  <div class="story-text">
    <mark>our story</mark>
    <h2 id="story-title">A small agency with big ambitions</h2>
    <p>
      KittyCode Creative is an East Sussex based web design and development
      agency, established in 2024. We're based in Eastbourne, but we work with
      clients anywhere in the world. No matter who you are or where you are, we
      always strive to offer the best possible service.
    </p>
    <p>
      We're led by Austin Spillman, a creative and passionate multi-disciplined
      digital designer and web developer with almost a decade of experience in
      the design and tech industry. That means your website is in safe, capable
      hands from the first conversation right through to launch and beyond.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every site we make is hand-coded from scratch using the latest web
      technologies, so it's genuinely one of a kind, fully <a href="/services"
        >accessible</a
      > and built to grow with you.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="story-media">
    <img
      src={kittyGif.src}
      width={kittyGif.width}
      height={kittyGif.height}
      alt="Animated KittyCode Creative cat"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #story {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    justify-items: stretch;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: start;
  }

  #story > :global(*) {
    margin-block-start: 0;
  }

  .story-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-text > :nth-child(2) {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .story-text > :nth-child(n + 3) {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-l);
  }

  #story p {
    max-inline-size: 68ch;
    text-align: start;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  #story p + p {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-s);
  }

  #story p a {
    color: inherit;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline 3px solid var(--primary);
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  #story p a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .story-media {
    justify-self: end;
  }

  .story-media img {
    inline-size: clamp(13.75rem, 28vw, 22.5rem);
    block-size: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius, 1rem);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #story {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      justify-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .story-text {
      align-items: center;
    }

    #story p {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .story-media {
      justify-self: center;
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
